Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveSinger, Harrysong, has lamented the endorsement deals he lost due to the activities of Internet fraudsters on his Instagram page.
Harrysong said this in a post on his Instagram Story on Monday.
He said that he lost the deals due to fear of the “yahoo boys” who he claimed had been trying to hack into his Instagram page.
“Just because of the fear of yahoo boys and fraudsters in my DM trying to hack my page, I missed 3 big endorsement deals. F**k mehn, I feel like biting someone’s ear right now,” he wrote.
